# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# NestIQ Backend — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── WhatsApp (Meta Cloud API) ──────────────────────
META_WHATSAPP_TOKEN=your_permanent_access_token
META_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=your_phone_number_id
META_WEBHOOK_VERIFY_TOKEN=nestiq_webhook_secret_2024
META_APP_SECRET=your_app_secret_for_signature_verification

# ── Anthropic Claude ───────────────────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── Google Calendar ────────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=GOCSPX-...
GOOGLE_REFRESH_TOKEN=1//your_refresh_token

# ── Supabase ───────────────────────────────────────
SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxxxxxxxxxx.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# ── Email (SMTP) ───────────────────────────────────
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your_16_char_app_password
AGENT_EMAIL=agent@youragency.com

# ── Agency Configuration ───────────────────────────
AGENCY_NAME=Lagos Property Group
AGENT_NAME=Sarah Adeyemi

# ── Server ─────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=3001
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
DASHBOARD_URL=http://localhost:5174
